headline: F5 Appoints Angelique Okeke as General Counsel
summary: SEATTLE, March 17, 2025--F5 (NASDAQ: FFIV) today announced the appointment of Angelique Okeke as Executive Vice President and General Counsel. Okeke succeeds Scot Rogers, who is departing after 20 years with the company.
